properties.Name: PackageMaterialType
properties.Description:
The type of package material used in constructing the packaging.

Ex:
- Bio-Plastic 
- Burlap 
- Composite 
- Corrugated 
- Corrugated Board 
- Double Wall Corrugated Board 
- Double-wall Paper 
- Fiberboard

- Not Otherwise Specified

- Polyethylene 
- Pulpboard 
- Single Wall Corrugated Board 
- Soft Wood
- Triple Wall Corrugated Board
- Wire Mesh
- Wood
